      "Supports": "Presentation with classic nephrotic syndrome (severe hypoalbuminemia, massive proteinuria, edema).",
      "Arguments against": "Less common in adults; usually presents with more sudden onset edema.",
      "Verdict": "Well-supported."
    },
    "Lupus membranous nephropathy": {
